Package transforma.qb2_user_app.quicabotAppLicence

This package is a collection of class related to licence page, it includes view adapter and licence content , you are suggested to know Android Recycler View before start amending the code.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppLicenceUsed
    Json Object class containing information about the 3rd party library we used for this project Changing format of this class requires corresponding change to be made to the recyclerViewAdapter
    LicencePageRecyclerViewAdapter
    This is the recyclerview adapter class for the licence page It binds the customised cardView to the recyclerView by passing in the licenceDate to the constructor No amendments to be made to this class if just simply adding more licence card to the page
    LicencePageRecyclerViewAdapter.MyViewHolder  
    QuicabotAppLicencePage
    This activity displays the 3rd party library used inside this project Format is fixed:

Package transforma.qb2_user_app.quicabotAppLicence Description

This package is a collection of class related to licence page, it includes view adapter and licence content , you are suggested to know Android Recycler View before start amending the code. If you just want to add in more app library that u used kindly go to Assets/Licence.csv and adding information there
